===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|ro der}}, {{m|enm|roadeor}}, from {{inh|en|ang|rāhdēor|t=roe deer}}, corresponding to {{m|en|roe}} + {{m|en|deer}}. Cognate with {{cog|is|rádýr}}, {{cog|sv|rådjur}}, {{cog|no|-}} and {{cog|da|rådyr}}.

